	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you can afford them, Gem Inlaid Gauntlets at around 100PP -- will last you forever (I still wear at 44), so make it an early upgrade.<br><br>If you can't afford them (and I couldn't until around level 20), just go down to Innothule Swamp or to Qeynos Sewers and kill Froglocks until you get a pair of Netted/Woven/Mesh gloves to drop.  They have only 2/3/4 AC respectively, but they ARE magic.  I killed about 50 Froglocks in Innothule and the first room in Upper Guk until Woven gloves dropped.<br>&nbsp;<br>Osano<br>Level 44 Human Monk<br>Tholuxe-Paells</td></tr>
