	   <tr><td colspan=2>There is no one answer to this question.  Not without knowing how much money you have.  You should be working towards a complete set of cured silk at a minimum.  Wu's armor if you have more money, with some exceptions - e.g. gem inlaid gauntlets, drolvarg mantle, foreman's tunic - all of which are better to have than Wu's and probably not much more expensive.  But like I said I can't say what you should have without knowing how much money you have.  At 13 I was pretty dirt-poor.  Others find ways (and make time) to gather good money.  <br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 46th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro <br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Strange Brew - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
