	   <tr><td colspan=2>By the way, the gypsy in North Karana isn't the only one you can trade greater lightstones to (and lightstones, though you only get a book worth about a gold, but you do get a nice chunk of exp at low levels).<br>I always used the gypsies in the oasis for this.  I suspect there's one female gypsy in every gypsy camp where this will work.  If I remember right only the one in North Karana will respond to hails and mention the Concordance of Research though, so you'd need to be able to pick out the one that looks the same.  Knowing that it's a female gypsy that's a vendor should narrow it down quite a bit.<br><br>Another note...you may not want to sell every Concordance of Research.  They appear to make very nice monk containers: 6 giant slots, weight 0.2.  No weight reduction, but a good replacement for the tailored large bags I used to use (6 large slots, 10% weight reduction--nearly useless for me, wt 0.8).<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
