	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.43]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Using ID on some of the slower MOBs is OK, even if not snared -- also, note that the lower on health a MOB is, the slower they will run when feared.  When soloing outdoors, sometimes I will only use ID in the second half of the battle, to try to save myself a little damage and reduce downtime.  As Keye noted, however, this skill is NOT for dungeons and is called 'Instill Train' there.<br><br>Gratz on 46 Keye -- how's the Raster hunt going?<br>&nbsp;<br>Osano<br>Level 44 Human Monk<br>Tholuxe-Paells</td></tr>
